## Slide 4: Dashboard KPI & Data Analytics Infrastructure

**Judul:** DASHBOARD KPI DAN STANDAR DATA: FOUNDATION FOR REAL-TIME ANALYTICS

---

### 📊 Current State: Static HTML Dashboard

**Existing Dashboard Analysis:**
- **Technology:** HTML5 + Chart.js + Bootstrap
- **Data:** Static/hardcoded values (simulasi Q2 2026)
- **Coverage:** 5 kategori dengan sample KPIs
- **Features:** Responsive design, trend analysis, alert system
- **Limitations:** No real-time integration, manual updates, limited scalability

**Dashboard Components Currently Available:**
✅ **Executive Summary:** Overall performance 82.3% (Target: 80%)
✅ **5 Strategic Categories:** Complete KPI coverage per category
✅ **Visual Analytics:** Line charts, radar charts, status indicators
✅ **Alert System:** Critical issue identification
✅ **Detailed Tables:** Month-by-month performance breakdown
✅ **Mobile Responsive:** Cross-device compatibility

### 🚀 Future State: Intelligent Analytics Platform

**Comprehensive Data Standards Development**

**1. Standard Data Model (2 Standar Documents)**
- **25+ Database Tables** dengan complete relationships
- **OLTP + OLAP Architecture** untuk transactional dan analytical processing
- **4-Layer Architecture:** Application → Business Logic → Integration → Storage
- **Technology Stack:** PostgreSQL + ClickHouse + Redis + Elasticsearch

**2. Metadata Schema (1 Standar Document)**
- **Business Metadata:** KPI definitions, business rules, data ownership
- **Technical Metadata:** Database schemas, API specs, integration patterns
- **Operational Metadata:** Data quality, usage statistics, performance metrics
- **Governance Metadata:** Data classification, access controls, compliance

### 📈 KPI Analytics Enhancement

**Current Dashboard → Future Analytics Platform**

| Capability | Current | Target |
|------------|---------|--------|
| **Data Sources** | Static HTML values | 15+ real-time integrated systems |
| **Update Frequency** | Manual updates | Real-time (<5 minutes) |
| **KPI Coverage** | Sample values | 149 complete KPIs |
| **Analytics Depth** | Basic visualization | Predictive analytics, AI insights |
| **User Experience** | Desktop-only | Mobile + desktop + API access |
| **Data Quality** | No validation | Automated quality monitoring (99% accuracy) |

### 🏗️ Technical Architecture

**4-Layer Data Architecture**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Presentation Layer                     │
│  ├── Real-time Dashboard                 │
│  ├── Mobile View                        │
│  ├── Export Reports                     │
│  └── Alert System                       │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Business Logic Layer                   │
│  ├── KPI Calculation Engine             │
│  ├── Data Validation Rules              │
│  ├── Aggregation & Roll-up              │
│  └── Trend Analysis                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Data Integration Layer                 │
│  ├── REST API Gateway                   │
│  ├── Data Transformation Services        │
│  ├── Scheduled Jobs                     │
│  └── Event Processing                   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Data Sources                           │
│  ├── INA-CRR System                     │
│  ├── CRU Management Systems             │
│  ├── Financial Systems                  │
│  ├── HR Training Systems                │
│  └── Manual Data Input                  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Performance Targets:**
- **Dashboard Load Time:** < 3 seconds
- **API Response Time:** < 500ms (95th percentile)
- **System Uptime:** > 99.5%
- **Data Processing Latency:** < 5 minutes for real-time KPIs

### 💰 Business Impact & ROI

**Quantified Benefits:**

**Immediate Benefits (Q1 2026):**
- **50% faster KPI access:** Hours → Minutes for decision making
- **100% audit readiness:** Complete audit trail and compliance
- **30% reduction in manual effort:** Automated data collection and reporting
- **Improved decision making:** Real-time data availability

**Financial Impact:**
- **Total Investment:** Rp 1.4B over 12 months
- **Annual Benefits:** Rp 3.6B (Rp 300M/month)
